          body:
            '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Welcome to the Dave Banking family!</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Your physical debit card will take about<strong> 7-10 business days</strong> <strong>to arrive.</strong></span></p>\n<p><em><strong>What if I haven\'t received my card and the 7-10 business days have passed? </strong></em></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We’re so sorry to hear you haven’t received your Dave debit card in the mail yet.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The good news is, we can help with re-issuing you another one! </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Simply reach out to us via </span><a href="https://banking.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360029560811" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>chat </strong></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">and we can take care of that for you.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Heads up! </strong>While you wait for your physical card to arrive, you can continue to pay online bills and make purchases using your <strong>virtual card</strong>.</span></p>\n<p> </p>',
