          sectionId: 360004817612,
          body:
            '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Need to<strong> load money</strong> into your Dave account?</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You can load funds to your Dave spending account a</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nywhere there is a <strong>Green Dot load network symbol.</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><em>(Participating retailers include Rite-Aid, Dollar General, and more!)</em></span></p>\n<p><strong><em>When will the deposit post to my account? </em></strong></p>\n<p>The retailer will be able to provide the funding timeframe. Some will also print the delay or processing timeframe on the receipt. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Check out this link for help finding a location nearest you:</strong></p>\n<p><a href="https://secure.attheregister.com/locations"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://secure.attheregister.com/locations</span></a></p>',
