          id: 360038692132,
          title: 'Get Paid Early ',
          sectionId: 360004817612,
          body:
            '<p>Unlike traditional banks, with a Dave spending account you have the ability to receive your direct deposit<strong> up to 2 days early</strong>! </p>\n<p>All you need to get started is to have your <strong>direct deposit going into your Dave Spending account</strong>. You can locate how to set up your direct deposit  <a href="https://banking.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360029502011" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here.</a> </p>\n<p class="p1">Just a heads up though,<strong> the exact timing of your deposit is dependent on your employer.</strong></p>\n<p class="p1">So if you aren\'t seeing your paycheck land up to 2 days early, we recommend reaching out to your employer to understand their payroll policies.</p>\n<p class="p1"> </p>\n<p> </p>',
