          title: 'Holidays',
          sectionId: 360004817612,
          body:
            "<p>Happy Holi-Daves!</p>\n<p>If you use Dave's spending account, during bank holidays, there may be a slight delay in the arrival of your direct deposit to your account... Or you may even get funds early! No need to fret, this is totally normal. </p>\n<p>It's always a good idea to confirm your direct deposit schedule with your employer during this season!</p>\n<p><em><strong>Please note,</strong> <strong>Dave will post funds as soon as we receive them from your employer. </strong></em></p>\n<p> </p>",
