          title: 'How do I qualify for $100 Advances? ',
          sectionId: 360004817612,
          body:
            '<p>One of the most amazing perks of being a Dave banking member is advancing up to $100!</p>\n<p>To qualify, please make sure you activate your Dave debit card and set up your direct deposits to post to your Dave spending account.</p>\n<p>Once you have at least <strong>two</strong> qualifying<a href="https://banking.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360029502011" target="_self"> direct deposit</a> in your Dave spending account, you\'ll see the option for $100 advances (as long as all other qualifications are met).</p>',
