          id: 360029502011,
          title: 'Adding direct deposit',
          sectionId: 360004817612,
          body:
            "<p>Direct deposits are an easy way to add funds into your Dave spending account. You'll also need to set up direct deposits to qualify for $100 advances.</p>\n<p><strong>How to add direct deposits:  </strong></p>\n<p>Tell your employer that you'd like to set up your paychecks as direct deposits (automatic, electronic transfers) and provide them with two things:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Your Dave banking<strong> account number </strong>\n</li>\n<li>Your <strong>routing number</strong>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>To find these numbers in your Dave app, go to the <strong>Banking</strong> tab and then select<strong> View account numbers.</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
