          title: 'How to transfer money ',
          sectionId: 360004817632,
          body:
            '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Transferring money from your linked bank is easy! </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Follow these steps and you\'ll be on your way: </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;">\n<span style="font-weight: 400;"> Select the </span><strong>Banking</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> tab</span>\n</li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;">\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Scroll and select </span><strong>Transfer Money</strong>\n</li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;">\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Select the </span><strong>external bank</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> you want to transfer funds </span><em><span style="font-weight: 400;">from</span></em>\n</li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;">\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Select the </span><strong>Dave account</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> as the recipient (</span><em><span style="font-weight: 400;">to</span></em><span style="font-weight: 400;">)</span>\n</li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Enter the amount you would like to transfer</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Keep in mind, </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">transfers made from within the Dave app are typically available in<strong> 4 to 5 business days. </strong></span></p>\n<p><em><strong>What if I want to send money from my Dave spending account to my linked bank? </strong></em></p>\n<p>No problem! Just pick your Dave spending account to transfer funds <strong>from</strong> and follow the same steps listed above. </p>',
