          title: 'How to dispute a transaction ',
          sectionId: 360004817632,
          body:
            '<p>Think something fishy is going on? If you suspect fraudulent activity on your card and want to dispute a charge, we have a few options for you.</p>\n<p>First, we recommend reaching out to the<strong> merchant</strong> to see if they can reverse any incorrect charges.</p>\n<p>If not, you can contact Dave ASAP and we\'ll get it sorted out. </p>\n<p>You can get a hold of us via chat through the app Monday-Saturday from 8:00 am - 4:00 pm PST or <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">email</a>. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>',
