          title: 'Receiving your Account Statement ',
          sectionId: 360004817672,
          body:
            '<p>Dave Banking<strong> paperless</strong> spending account statements are sent out on<strong> the third of every month</strong> via email.</p>\n<p><em><strong>What if I need a paper copy? </strong></em></p>\n<p>Though we do not offer paper statements, your account statement is attached as a PDF on the monthly email, you can both download or print your statement. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>',
