      title: 'Card expiring too soon ',
      sectionId: 115000397452,
      body:
        '<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What does this mean?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>Looks like your card is expiring soon. Check your expiration date -- if your card expires in up to three months or less, we can\'t process an advance.</p>\n<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What should you do?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>You\'ll need to get a new debit card that doesn\'t expire for at least up to three months. Then, you can easily update your card in the app by following the steps here: <strong><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360012683771-How-to-update-your-debit-card">How to Update Your Debit Card </a></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>',
