      title: '"Time outside ACH collection window"',
      sectionId: 115000397452,
      body:
        '<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What does this mean?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>We can only accept Automated Clearing House payments Monday through Thursday.</p>\n<p>If you\'re getting this error message, you\'re probably trying to process an ACH payment on a Friday, Saturday or Sunday (which is outside of the ACH collection window). </p>\n<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What should you do?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>Take the weekend off and try again on Monday, when you\'ll be good to go! </p>',
