      sectionId: 115000397452,
      body:
        '<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What does this mean?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>Your signature doesn\'t match what was saved under your Dave profile.</p>\n<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What should you do?</span></strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Make sure there is a space between your first and last name</li>\n<li>Check to see how your name is saved, you can find it on the <strong>Account</strong> tab by selecting <strong>Update your information</strong> under Settings</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Still having problems with your signature being accepted? Please <strong><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new">message</a></strong> customer support.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>',
