      title: 'Can I pay back early? ',
      sectionId: 115000397432,
      body:
        '<p>Of course! Dave loves early paybacks!</p>\n<p>You can pay Dave before your payback date with a partial or full payback by going to the "<strong>Account</strong>" tab, clicking "<strong>Advances</strong>" section, and then clicking on your current outstanding advance.</p>\n<p><strong>Heads up!</strong> If you choose a partial payback, the remaining balance will still be automatically pulled from your account on your original payback date. </p>\n<p>Once the full amount of your payback processes (1-3 business days), you\'re free to request another advance. </p>\n<p> </p>',
