      id: 360025568071,
      title: 'Dave Rewards ',
      sectionId: 115000397352,
      body:
        '<p>Want to earn credits to use towards a free Dave membership? <strong>Here\'s how:</strong></p>\n<p>1. Head to the <strong>Account </strong>tab in-app and select <strong>Dave rewards, earn free months </strong>under the "Dave Membership" section</p>\n<p>2. Link your debit card </p>\n<p>3. Earn credit with a qualifying purchase at any of our partner locations</p>\n<h3><strong>Hot tip</strong></h3>\n<p>Search for Dave partners in the area by enabling your location or searching for the desired zip code. </p>\n<h3><strong>Heads up</strong></h3>\n<p>Credits may take up to<strong> 3 business days</strong> to be reflected in the progress bar. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>',
