      id: 360003094611,
      title: 'Notifications',
      sectionId: 115000397352,
      body:
        "<p>Dave texts you alerts if something like an upcoming Netflix bill will put you in danger of a $35 overdraft fee. It's the fastest way for us to help you prevent those expensive (and unnecessary) bank fees.</p>\n<p><strong>Want to turn off your notifications? </strong>We think they're helpful, but<strong> </strong>it's easy to manage your alerts in-app.</p>\n<p>Just head over to the <strong>Account</strong> tab and click on <strong>Manage notifications. </strong></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"> </p>",
