      sectionId: 360003972191,
      body:
        "<p><strong>Using Dave won't have any impact on your credit score</strong>,<strong> </strong>positive or negative. </p>\n<p>We also don't do a credit pull, not even a soft one. The information you provide is only used to verify your identity. So, your credit is completely unaffected. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
