      title: 'How do I change my phone number?',
      sectionId: 115000397352,
      body:
        '<p>Get a new number? No problem! It\'s easy to update your digits. </p>\n<p>If you\'re currently logged out, follow these easy steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Select <strong>Log in </strong>\n</li>\n<li>Click <strong>I have a new number</strong> </li>\n<li>Enter your previous number &amp; your new number</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Submit</strong> </li>\n<li>You will get a text to confirm this change, be sure to <strong>enter the code provided</strong> in-app</li>\n<li>Visit your email to <strong>confirm</strong> this change</li>\n</ol>\n<p data-id="block-ember6221" data-generated-at="15046491530280.4993438354041533" data-align="left">If you\'re currently logged in, follow these steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the Account tab</li>\n<li>Scroll to <strong>Settings</strong> and click<strong> Update personal information</strong>\n</li>\n<li>Click the pencil icon next to<strong> Mobile number</strong>\n</li>\n<li>Enter the new phone number and click <strong>Verify</strong>\n</li>\n<li>You will get a text to confirm this change, be sure to <strong>enter the code provided</strong> in-app</li>\n<li>Visit your email to <strong>confirm</strong> this change</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>',
