      title: 'When will I be charged my membership fee?',
      sectionId: 115000397352,
      body:
        '<p>It\'s super easy to check when you\'ll be charged next:</p>\n<ol class="ol1">\n<li class="li1">Head to the <strong>Account</strong> section in-app</li>\n<li class="li1">Under Dave Membership click <strong>Manage membership</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Heads up! </strong>The $1 monthly membership fee is to connect your bank account to our prediction tool (so we can text you alerts) and isn\'t related to advancing your paycheck. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><em><strong> </strong></em></p>',
