          title: 'Forgot Password ',
          sectionId: 115000397212,
          body:
            '<p>Uh oh! Can\'t remember your password?  No biggie, here\'s how to update your password:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Open up the Dave app and click <strong>Log In</strong>\n</li>\n<li>Select the <strong>With Email</strong> tab and click "<strong>Forgot password?"</strong>\n</li>\n<li>Enter your registered email and click <strong>Send Login Link</strong>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Go ahead and check your email and you should be good to go to create a new password by clicking the <strong>Change your password </strong>button. </p>\n<p>Still running into an issue? Go ahead and reach out to support <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>.</p>',
