          id: 360032392652,
          title: 'Paused Membership',
          sectionId: 115000397352,
          body:
            '<p class="p1">We totally understand if you want to part ways from Dave. But, before you go, remember there\'s the option to pause your membership.</p>\n<ol>\n<li class="p1">Go to the <strong>Account</strong> tab on the app.</li>\n<li class="p1">Select <strong>Manage membership</strong> under the <strong>Dave Membership </strong>section</li>\n<li class="p1"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Click<strong> View membership status </strong></span></li>\n<li class="p1"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Select <strong>Manage Membership</strong></span></li>\n<li class="p1"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Scroll to the bottom of the screen and click<strong> Pause membership</strong></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p class="p1">Dave won\'t charge you a subscription while your membership is paused and you can unpause in-app at any time! </p>',
