          id: 360001347071,
          title: 'How do I contact Dave?',
          sectionId: 115000397352,
          body:
            '<p class="wysiwyg-text-align-left"><strong>For immediate help, check out our</strong> <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Help Center</strong></a> for answers to our most commonly asked questions.</p>\n<p><strong>Need to talk to someone? </strong>No worries, we\'re happy to help!</p>\n<p>Contact us via a secure<strong> <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">message</a> </strong>and a friend from customer service should get back to you within 24 hours.</p>',
