          id: 360001394491,
          title: 'Why are my transactions not updating?',
          sectionId: 115000397352,
          body:
            '<p>Hmm. Have you tried refreshing your account by sliding down the home screen?</p>\n<p>If you still don\'t see your transactions, we could be experiencing a lag with your bank.</p>\n<p>We rely on banks to send us your information but sometimes, with smaller banks and credit unions, there are delays. Most banks send us data in less than 30 minutes but others can take hours, days, or might not send us anything at all. </p>\n<p>We constantly check for updates (<em>anywhere from 4-6 times a day</em>). So, when your bank is ready to send your data, we\'ll be ready and waiting! </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class="wysiwyg-text-align-center"> </p>',
