          id: 115001436231,
          title: 'Can I share a bank account with another Dave user?',
          sectionId: 115000397352,
          body:
            '<p>Sharing is caring...except when it comes to your account.</p>\n<p>For security reasons, <strong>we only support one Dave account per user.</strong></p>\n<p>We don\'t support joint bank accounts or shared Dave accounts. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>We also only allow one device per Dave account and one Dave account per bank account.</p>\n<p data-id="block-ember7288" data-generated-at="15046496525830.0460390071555401" data-align="left"><strong>Heads up!</strong> Duplicate accounts will be flagged and won\'t be eligible for advances. </p>\n<p data-id="block-ember7288" data-generated-at="15046496525830.0460390071555401" data-align="left">If you\'re still having an issue, send us a <strong><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new">secure message</a></strong> and we\'ll get it sorted out. </p>',
