          sectionId: 115000397452,
          body:
            '<h2> <strong>Why are you getting this error message? </strong>\n</h2>\n<p>It looks like your debit card has already been used for a previous Dave account (whether it\'s active or not).</p>\n<p>Most likely, you got a new phone number and this card is still associated with your old account. </p>\n<h2><strong>What can you do?</strong></h2>\n<p><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new"><strong>Message support</strong></a> and we\'ll get it sorted out for you. </p>\n<p> </p>',
