          title:
            '"Sorry, but you\'ve got to wait -- more days before I can let you back in. It costs us money when you delete/rejoin."',
          sectionId: 115000397452,
          body:
            '<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What does this mean?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>Since it costs us money when users delete and rejoin Dave, we have a two-month waiting period before users can reactivate their account after canceling it.</p>\n<p>We\'d love to help but it looks like you\'ve deleted your account and the waiting period isn\'t quite up yet. </p>\n<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What should you do?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>Check back again once your waiting period is over. </p>\n<p>We\'re looking forward to outsmarting overdrafts together soon!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>',
