          title: '"I\'m still waiting on your last payment to clear."',
          sectionId: 115000397452,
          body:
            '<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What does this mean?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>It takes us between 1-3 business days for your payment to clear through our bank. Until then, we are unable to provide another advance. </p>\n<h2><strong><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large">What should you do?</span></strong></h2>\n<p>Sit back, turn on <strong><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360003094611" target="_blank" rel="noopener">notifications</a></strong> and relax! We\'ll notify you once you\'re able to advance again (or you can always check back again later in the app).</p>',
