          sectionId: 115000397452,
          body:
            "<h2><strong>What does this mean? </strong></h2>\n<p>Oops, we need your real mobile phone number digits! Dave can't accept VoIP numbers or burners. </p>\n<h2><strong>What can you do? </strong></h2>\n<p>Double-check that you've entered your correct phone number and try again! </p>\n<h3><strong>Still having issues?</strong></h3>\n<p>Send a <a href=\"https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new\"><strong>message</strong></a> to support and we'll help you sort it out.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
