          sectionId: 360003972191,
          body:
            '<p>Though we appreciate your tip, if you did not mean to tip or want to adjust the amount<strong> before</strong> your payback date, follow these simple steps below: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open the Dave app and click the <strong>Account tab</strong>\n</li>\n<li>On the top left-hand corner, click <strong>Advances </strong>\n</li>\n<li>Under <strong>Current</strong>, select your open <strong>advance </strong>\n</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Pay Dave Back</strong> <em>(no need to worry, this will not trigger a payment right away!) </em>\n</li>\n<li>Select <strong>Optional tip</strong> and update to your desired amount </li>\n</ul>\n<p class="p2">For every % you tip, we donate to our partners<a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360039864411" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Feeding America</a> or <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001144471" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Trees for the future!</a></p>\n<p class="p2">Click <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360002647991" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> to find out more. </p>\n<p class="p2">Still having trouble updating your tip? Just <strong><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">send us a message</a></strong> and we\'ll get it sorted out.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class="p2"> </p>',
