          title: '11 Days Away ',
          sectionId: 360003972191,
          body:
            '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As our mission at Dave is to help combat overdraft fees and keep members from falling into debt, </span>Dave can only give advances within<strong> 11 days</strong> of when your next scheduled direct deposit arrives. </p>\n<p><strong>Be sure to</strong> <strong>enable push and/or text notifications!</strong> That way you\'ll be notified as soon as you are in the clear to determine your advance eligibility. </p>\n<p><em><strong>Wondering how to get approved for an advance once you are within 11 days of your next direct deposit? </strong></em></p>\n<p>Click<a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> here</a> for more information! </p>',
