      title: 'How do I change my bank? ',
      sectionId: 115000397352,
      body:
        '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Need to change your bank account?</strong> No problem. You can change your bank information right through the app! </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you currently have an advance with Dave,</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> <strong>you\'ll be able to change banks once your balance has been cleared. </strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Keep in mind,</strong> once you switch bank accounts, you will lose all of the information you’ve set for your budget and income. Not a big deal, it\'s super easy to get set up again. <br><br>You\'ll also need to go through the </span><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532-How-do-I-get-approved-for-a-regular-advance-"><strong>advance approval process </strong></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">again. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Heads up:</strong> we\'ll need to see at least<strong> 2 direct deposits</strong> into your <strong>new</strong> bank account before we can approve you for an advance.</span></p>\n<h2><strong>Steps to change your bank: </strong></h2>\n<ol>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Go to the <strong>Account</strong> tab</span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Click on your bank under <strong>Connected Account &amp; Card</strong></span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">There, you’ll see an option to <strong>Change bank</strong></span></li>\n<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Select your new bank and enter your new login information</span></li>\n</ol>',
