          body:
            '<p><strong>How It Works</strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Daves helps you budget for upcoming expenses and texts you if you’re in danger of overdraft. And if you need cash fast, we’ll advance you up to $75 at </span><strong>0% interest</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;">! No credit check required.</span> </p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tips are optional but they do help us provide services to millions of other Dave members. So, if Dave helped you out with an advance, show him some love!</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Plus, with every % you tip, we plant a tree or provide a meal to a child through our partnerships with <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001144471" target="_self">Trees For The Future</a> and <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360039864411" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Feeding America</a>.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>What’s the catch?</strong> There isn’t one! A $1 per month membership fee provides you with potential overdraft protection through cash advances, automatic budgeting tools, and access to jobs.</span></p>\n<p><strong>Membership fees are just</strong> <strong>$1/ month</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;">. This helps us offset the costs of offering predictive texts and connecting to your bank (we get charged every time we connect). </span></p>\n<p><strong>Predictive Texts</strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Dave securely connects to your</span><strong> checking account </strong><span style="font-weight: 400;">to help you track your expenses. Then, we’ll send text alerts if your account looks low or if an upcoming bill (like Netflix) puts you in danger of overdraft. </span></p>\n<p><strong>Advances </strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Need cash fast? Dave can spot you <strong>one advance at a time</strong>. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532?flash_digest=b01e03347a5a3484e1d168b83fb785c16d7eef19">Qualified users</a></strong> can get <strong>up to $75</strong> delivered into their checking account in just a couple of days or even </span><em><span style="font-weight: 400;">hours</span></em><span style="font-weight: 400;"> (for a small fee if you choose our express option). </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Getting an advance doesn’t impact your credit</strong> and there are <strong>no late fees or penalties</strong> (we’re friends, remember!). </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">However, it’s your responsibility to pay Dave back by your due date, which will be confirmed in the app. Otherwise, you’ll risk being banned from the app. And no one wants that! </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Heads up! The $1 monthly membership fee is strictly to connect your bank account to the prediction tool and does not have an association with qualifying for an advance.</strong></span></p>\n<p>Here are some helpful links to help you get started:</p>\n<table class="t1 wysiwyg-text-align-center" style="height: 402px;" width="281" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<h1 class="p1 wysiwyg-text-align-left"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532?flash_digest=b01e03347a5a3484e1d168b83fb785c16d7eef19"><strong>Helpful Links</strong></a></h1>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<p class="p2"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532?flash_digest=b01e03347a5a3484e1d168b83fb785c16d7eef19"><span class="s1">Sign up &amp; Login</span></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<p class="p2"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532?flash_digest=b01e03347a5a3484e1d168b83fb785c16d7eef19"><span class="s1">Cost</span></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<p class="p2"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532?flash_digest=b01e03347a5a3484e1d168b83fb785c16d7eef19"><span class="s1">Tipping</span></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<p class="p2"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532?flash_digest=b01e03347a5a3484e1d168b83fb785c16d7eef19"><span class="s1">Predictions</span></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<p class="p2"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016519532?flash_digest=b01e03347a5a3484e1d168b83fb785c16d7eef19"><span class="s1">Qualifying for a Regular Advance</span></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<p class="p2"><span class="s1"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001119352-Delivery-options">Delivery Options</a></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<p class="p2"><span class="s1"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001141671-How-do-I-pay-Dave-back-">Paying Dave back</a></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class="td1 wysiwyg-text-align-left" style="width: 277.778px;" valign="top">\n<p class="p2"><span class="s1"><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001266792-Can-I-trust-Dave-with-my-bank-information-">Security</a></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>',
