          sectionId: 360003972191,
          body:
            '<p> </p>\n<p><strong>1.</strong> Open the Dave app </p>\n<p><strong>2</strong>. Click the<strong> Advances</strong> tab at the bottom the screen</p>\n<p><strong>3</strong>. Click the account you would like to send your advance to </p>\n<p><strong>4.</strong> Choose the amount of money that you\'d like to request<strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong>5.</strong> Verify your identity (if you\'re a first-time user)</p>\n<p><strong>6.</strong> Confirm your payback date </p>\n<p><strong>7.</strong> Choose your delivery option (<strong>free standard delivery</strong> in up to 3 business days or <strong>express delivery</strong> in up to 8 hours for a small fee)</p>\n<p>8. Update the<strong> tip amount</strong> if you like </p>\n<p><strong>9.</strong> Check that the <strong>last 4</strong> digits of your debit card are correct.</p>\n<p><strong>10.</strong> Click the box to agree to the payment authorization </p>\n<p><strong>11.</strong> Sign and confirm!</p>\n<p><span class="wysiwyg-color-black"><strong>Tip:</strong> </span>Double-check your information and<strong> make sure your payback date is correct. </strong>Once you confirm your advance, your payback date is locked in and can\'t be changed later. </p>\n<p><strong>11.</strong> Leave a <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360002647991-Tipping">tip</a> if Dave helped! </p>\n<p>Donations help us stay in business<em> and</em> we plant a tree with the amount that you tip! Learn more about the power of tipping<strong> <a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/articles/360002647991-Tipping">here</a></strong>. </p>\n<p>  </p>\n<p> </p>',
