          title: 'When will I get my advance?',
          sectionId: 360003972191,
          body:
            '<p>When you request your advance in the app, you\'ll see two delivery options:</p>\n<h3><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large"><strong>Standard</strong></span></h3>\n<p>Free! Standard advances take up to 3 business days (<strong>example:</strong> an advance requested on Friday arrives the following Wednesday)</p>\n<h3><span class="wysiwyg-font-size-large"><strong>Express</strong></span></h3>\n<p>Small Fee and arrives in less than 8 hours!</p>\n<p><strong>Heads up! Once your advance has been confirmed, we\'re unable to change your delivery speed. </strong></p>\n<p>Standard advances will be delivered into your checking account and Express advances will be delivered to your connected debit card. BAM – money. How easy is that? </p>\n<p><strong>Having trouble?</strong> </p>\n<p>Send us <strong><a href="https://support.dave.com/hc/en-us/requests/new">a message</a></strong> and we\'ll get to the bottom of it. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>',
